制造的白 T。店铺位于三里屯 3.3 大厦一层，面积近百平米，延续了纯白极简风格。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190508153613BkYPVl8JdURg6FQu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750179\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190508153626T9h4RCNIW1mF3KLJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.599809\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190508153626tXRm5xSkMoABT1F9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.599809\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190508153630Bt1vDVAyQM0oR5pr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190508153647hRyzPjilk8KEW4Id.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.640777\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://metalmagazine.eu/en/post/editorial/my-willing-heart-giuseppe-triscari\" rel=\"nofollow\"><em>Metal Magazine</em> 造型特辑：My willing heart。</a></strong><br></p><p>摄影：Giuseppe Triscari，造型：Giorgia Toscani。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190508151306cOHa9FzQTvtD1fdP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.273885\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190508151305hHjUmYvA879gCdo6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.270850\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190508151302OcowRQq2JgFvYN97.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.283079\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190508151305L048hPHepBNZ1Y5d.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.282051\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190508151304zn7d853vmw4TFJEf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.282051\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201905081513038cmF3QzS2gZuGaU1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.314708\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"